data.description: This stunning 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home is situated in the beautiful Seacrest Estates. This home features a brand new roof, hurricane impact windows and doors, and new A/C. This home has been tastefully updated with loads of character. Great sized bedrooms, plenty of closet space, private sanctuary area off the master, great kitchen space with white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances with an eat-in kitchen area. Backyard is completely fenced with fruit trees and has a storage room connected to the home, along with separate storage shed. This backyard is cozy and is perfect for family gatherings and entertainment.
